.container
  .row
    .span12
      .well
        h2 Instructions
        p Welcome bloody pirates! Pillage towns and sink ships to become the most notorious pirate captain!
        p Use WASD to move and the left mouse button to attack ships and pillage towns.
        p You have 5 minutes to get as many notoriety points as you can. You gain notoriety by pillaging towns, attacking ships, and sinking ships. You get double the points while you have the treasure chest. The player holding the treasure gets a 300 point bonus at the end of the game.

        h2 Lobbies
        ul.unstyled
          li(ng-repeat='(id, lobby) in lobbies')
            a(href ng-click='joinLobby(id)') {{lobby.name}} [{{lobby.players.length}}/4]
        hr
        fieldset
          label New Lobby Name
          input(ng-model='newLobbyName')
          p  
          button.btn(ng-click='newLobby()') Start a New Lobby
    //-
      .span6
        .well
          h2 Chat
          p chat over here, maybe?
          form(ng-submit='sendMassage()')
            input(ng-model='newChatMessage')
            | 
            button.btn(type='submit') Send
